  "content": "<p></p><h1 class=\"title\">Mhar</h1><h2><b>The World Thunder</b></h2><b>Source</b> <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://paizo.com/products/btpy9nry?Pathfinder-Adventure-Path-109-In-Search-of-Sanity\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Pathfinder #109: In Search of Sanity pg. 68</i></a><br /><b>Pathfinder Wiki</b> <a href=\"http://www.pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Mhar\">Mhar</a><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Details</h3><p><b>Alignment</b> CN<br /><b>Pantheon</b> Great Old Ones<br /><b>Areas of Concern</b> Caverns, mountains, volcanoes<br /><b>Domains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Chaos\">Chaos</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Destruction\">Destruction</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Earth\">Earth</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Fire\">Fire</a><br /><b>Subdomains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Fire\">Ash</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Destruction\">Catastrophe</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Earth\">Caves</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Fire\">Smoke</a><br /><i>* Requires the <u><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Acolyte%20of%20Apocrypha\">Acolyte of Apocrypha</a></u> trait.</i><br /><b>Favored Weapon</b> Heavy pick<br /><b>Symbol</b> Shattered triangular rune<br /><b>Sacred Animal(s)</b> None<br /><b>Sacred Color(s)</b> Black, orange<br /></p><h2 class=\"title\">For Followers of Mhar</h2><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Feats</h3><p><a href=\"FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Dreamed Secrets\">Dreamed Secrets</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Magic Items - Wondrous Items</h3><p><a href=\"MagicWondrousDisplay.aspx?FinalName=Preklikin's Book of Cults\">Preklikin's Book of Cults</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Traits</h3><p><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Unspeakable Bond\">Unspeakable Bond</a><br /><br /></p><div style=\"position:relative;left:0%;border:2px ridge #434343;width:100%;height:100%\"><div class=\"wiki-content-full\"><iframe style=\"overflow-y:hidden;width:100%;height:450px\" src=\"https://pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Mhar\"> </iframe></div>\n </div>",
